{"tid":497340,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星，有冇人返工就成日放屁？","createTime":"2017-12-12T15:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T16:58:58.000Z","uid":27396,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30dc3d1e69f5b87149a4f2dad12455bfbbfc3f0e","tid":497340,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"一返工行兩步就一個屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排仲要腸胃差，係咁放濕屁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老闆呢幾日開始問我地聞唔聞到啲怪味，咁啱隔<br />\n離有間茶記裝修，搞到好大塵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老闆今日嬲到去屌7佢地話搞到成陣味，仲差啲同<br />\n啲裝修佬隻抽，要成班男同事㩒住佢先得。<br />\n<br />\n聽日老闆話班裝修佬再係咁就唔忍，我應該點做先<br />\n好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543064890f861a5c9fcc20c5ae20478c4b05346c","tid":497340,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61393a17866e246bf0d4af23d68220a2605cc40c","tid":497340,"uid":109768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"食多d蕃薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1e6f20725c1f70733d10a558b59c3b0d2a21c3","tid":497340,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食多d蕃薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我驚放到痴線<br />\n呢家都成日忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc81704ef2f621d78049ab9a08b81cdb65009a8","tid":497340,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食多d蕃薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我驚放到痴線<br />\n呢家都成日忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔清乾淨腸胃, 永遠都臭"},{"pid":"7b229a5ce64dbd9daf17d63aa8b45a378d929f83","tid":497340,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"飲夏枯草"},{"pid":"415159afdd280b9c4fce0c5cf2aee18d57aca228","tid":497340,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食多d蕃薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我驚放到痴線<br />\n呢家都成日忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔清乾淨腸胃, 永遠都臭</blockquote><br />\n我鍾意食辣野關唔關事？"},{"pid":"d33083aea8985860aa0a131df189c89044821d1c","tid":497340,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲夏枯草</blockquote><br />\n有用咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d1bc871ca59146d362826e5e68bcc087e84720","tid":497340,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"試下返工前入去格離幫裝修佬做下野先<br />\n等佢地頂唔順打左你老闆先"},{"pid":"ba20ce7a3b2f07b9acb1acdf4b94d8fe66e868ca","tid":497340,"uid":55552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/005854_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F005854_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c15a022e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}